Author: 	mbergmann-sh@web.de (Michael Bergmann)
Type: 		dev/c
Version: 	1.0
Architecture: 	m68k-amigaos
Replaces: 	
Requires: 	ixemul.library
Distribution: 	Aminet
Kurz: 		programmiere farbige Textzeilen in C


ShellColors demonstrates how to set certain text attributes in C.

Tested C-Compilers:
===================
SAS/C v6.58
VBCC v0.9h
Bebbo's amiga-gcc

USAGE
=====
simply include shellattrs.h in your project. Look at
color.c for a usage example.

